<li id="cite_note-42"><b><a href="#cite_ref-42" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=6FKHIeUQ2J0C&amp;pg=PA284&amp;dq=%22common+era+of+the+foundation+of+rome%22" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=6FKHIeUQ2J0C&amp;pg=PA284&amp;dq=%22common+era+of+the+foundation+of+rome%22" rel="nofollow">""common era of the foundation of Rome" (1854)"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=6FKHIeUQ2J0C&amp;pg=PA284&amp;dq=%22common+era+of+the+foundation+of+rome%22" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=6FKHIeUQ2J0C&amp;pg=PA284&amp;dq=%22common+era+of+the+foundation+of+rome%22" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=6FKHIeUQ2J0C&amp;pg=PA284&amp;dq=%22common+era+of+the+foundation+of+rome%22</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-12-13</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=%22common+era+of+the+foundation+of+Rome%22+%281854%29&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D6FKHIeUQ2J0C%26pg%3DPA284%26dq%3D%2522common%2Bera%2Bof%2Bthe%2Bfoundation%2Bof%2Brome%2522&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Common_Era"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFAlexander_Fraser_Tytler.2C_Lord_Woodhouselee1854">Alexander Fraser Tytler, Lord Woodhouselee (1854). <i>Universal History: From the Creation of the World to the Beginning of the Eighteenth Century</i>. Boston: Fetridge and Company. pp.&#160;284.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Universal+History%3A+From+the+Creation+of+the+World+to+the+Beginning+of+the+Eighteenth+Century&amp;rft.aulast=Alexander+Fraser+Tytler%2C+Lord+Woodhouselee&amp;rft.au=Alexander+F